  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser initially requested a presentation about the 7d LIFE coaching project but pivoted to requesting a functional web app instead. Manus successfully built a complete beta version featuring the 7-petal Flower of Life model with user authentication, database integration, assessments, goal setting, weekly tracking, and animated visualization dashboard. The app includes core functionality for holistic wellness coaching with 0-10 scoring system and chakra-based dimensions.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nDevelop a functional beta version of the 7d LIFE coaching application for team testing, moving beyond presentation materials to an interactive web platform\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nBuilt complete web application with user authentication, database schema, onboarding flow, baseline assessment system, animated flower visualization, 90-day goal setting with micro-actions, and weekly tracking with daily metrics\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [web_application] 7d LIFE Beta App — Fully functional coaching app with authentication, assessments, and progress tracking\n- [database_schema] Application Database — Complete data architecture supporting user profiles, assessments, goals, and tracking\n- [ui_components] Interactive Dashboard — Animated 7-petal flower visualization and detailed petal pages\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Pivot from presentation to functional app\n- Implement complete authentication system\n- Use 7-petal Flower of Life as core visualization\n- Include 90-day goal framework with micro-actions\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Clear project pivot from presentation to functional app\n- Comprehensive feature implementation in single development cycle\n- Integration of holistic wellness model with technical architecture\nDiscoveries:\n\n- User preference for functional prototype over presentation materials\n- Effectiveness of chakra-based wellness framework for app structure\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Add data visualization charts for progress trends\n- Implement email notification system for weekly reminders\n- Create export and sharing features for user reports\n---\nUID: cxVhUQ3Cu937dAwZd4Vyn5 | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0132\n"
